OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fblustery showers, some of the showers
OL,7,Flocally heavy with a risk of hail and
OL,8,Fthunder. Feeling rather cold, with
OL,9,Ftemperatures below average for the
OL,10,Ftime of year.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPatchy cloud with further
OL,13,Fshowers into the evening and
OL,14,Fovernight. Temperatures falling to low
OL,15,Fsingle figures but remaining generally
OL,16,Ffrost free.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
