OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAnother day of bright spells
OL,6,Fand occasional heavy showers, these
OL,7,Fcontinuing to bring the risk of some
OL,8,Fhail and thunder. Turning generally
OL,9,Fdrier through the evening.
OL,10,FTemperatures remaining cool.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDrier
OL,13,Finto Friday and Saturday, sunny spells
OL,14,Fbut temperatures a little below
OL,15,Faverage. Likely cloudier Sunday with
OL,16,Fsome rain possible, but temperatures
OL,17,Fturning milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
